<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> For example, in the Arabic world, much diplomacy was carried out through poetic form in the 16th century. <i>See</i> Natalie Zemon Davis. <i>Trickster's Travels</i>. Hill &amp; Wang, (2006), <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0809094355" class="internal">ISBN 0809094355</a>.</li>
