<li id="cite_note-15"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15" title="">^</a></b> In <a href="/wiki/Ancient_Greece" title="Ancient Greece">ancient Greece</a>, medical and scholarly works were often written in metrical form. A millennium and a half later, many of <a href="/wiki/Avicenna" title="Avicenna">Avicenna</a>'s medical texts were written in verse.</li>
